data.name: $FILE_ID
data.comment: {locked} This is the file ID for this localization file. This string value should not be used or translated.

data.name: errorLoadingDebugScriptHTTPS
data.value: Error loading debug script. Ensure the server is running and the "{0}" parameter URL is correct.
data.comment: A message to print when an error occurs while loading debug scripts. The {0} placeholder represents the paramter containing the URL.

data.name: errorLoadingDebugScriptHTTP
data.value: Error loading debug script. Ensure the server is running, the "{0}" parameter URL is correct, and loading unsafe scripts is allowed. Also consider using a development certificate and serving debug scripts over HTTPS.
data.comment: A message to print when an error occurs while loading debug scripts. "HTTPS" is a protocol and should be localized. The {0} placeholder represents the paramter containing the URL.

data.name: errorLoadingDebugScriptMalformed
data.value: Error loading debug script. The debug URL ({0}) appears to be malformed.
data.comment: A message to print when an error occurs while loading debug scripts. The {0} placeholder is the malformed URL.

data.name: errorLoadingDebugScriptUnknown
data.value: Unknown error loading a debug script.
data.comment: A message to print when an unknown error occurs while loading debug scripts.

data.name: errorLoadingDebugLoaderTitle
data.comment: The title of a dialog notifying the user that the debug loader failed to load.

data.name: errorLoadingDebugManifestTitle
data.comment: The title of a dialog notifying the user that debug manifests failed to load.

data.name: errorLoadingUnknownTitle
data.comment: The title of a dialog notifying the user that an unknwon error has occurred loading debug scripts.
